summary: First reaction when I saw the Gucci pic of harry and the chx: wow! What a cool manip! Lol. And then my mouth fell open as I...
question: First reaction when I saw the Gucci pic of harry and the chx: wow! What a cool manip! Lol. And then my mouth fell open as I scrolled and realized this was not #fakenews but in fact I was viewing harrys Gucci pics. He’s a beautiful man. I don’t know how else to describe it. And something about those pics - there’s like a light in them that gives me this quirky happy vibe. I dunno. Lol.
answer:
Luckily I had a few people message me this morning to warn of the onslaught of Harry-filled deliciousness I was about to face…!

He is absolutely beautiful, and I really love the three pictures we have. Love the atmosphere they invoke, love the clothes, love the chicken, love the Harry…and of course I love the real stars of the show - the Gucci pups.

tags: maybe i'm late to the party with this interview
but there aren't many musicians who see things that way
summary: Styles is aware that his largest audience so far has been young – often teenage – women. Asked if he spends pressure-filled...
body:
Styles is aware that his largest audience so far has been young – often teenage – women. Asked if he spends pressure-filled evenings worried about proving credibility to an older crowd, Styles grows animated. “Who’s to say that young girls who like pop music – short for popular, right? – have worse musical taste than a 30-year-old hipster guy? That’s not up to you to say. Music is something that’s always changing. There’s no goal posts. Young girls like the Beatles. You gonna tell me they’re not serious? How can you say young girls don’t get it? They’re our future. Our future doctors, lawyers, mothers, presidents, they kind of keep the world going. Teenage-girl fans – they don’t lie. If they like you, they’re there. They don’t act ‘too cool.’ They like you, and they tell you. Which is sick.”

God bless Harry Styles for having this attitude towards teen fans
